   PUPIL _ AUSTIN, Texas _ If anyone has doubted the cultlike
fascination ``The Usual Suspects'' exerted on a generation of teen
and twenty-something film dweebs, they need only to have witnessed
the scene in the lobby of the Paramount last Thursday after the
screening of Bryan Singer's latest flick, ``Apt Pupil.'' This is
