<HEADLINE>
EDITORS: 
  
</HEADLINE>
  
 Friday, Oct. 16, 1998
<TEXT>
<P>
   The Hearst News Service will file the following stories for
Saturday and Sunday. If you have questions, call Tim Spence at
202-298-6920. &LR;  &QL;
