<HEADER>
A0859 &Cx1f; tad-z
u l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-RELIGION-ADVISORY-COX     10-16 0179
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-RELIGION-ADVISORY-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;    
 &HT;    
 &HT;    EDITORS:
 &HT;   
