   TERRORISM-OFFICE (Washington) _ Attorney General Janet Reno
announces the creation of a new office that will focus on domestic
terrorism. By STEVE LASH.
</P>
<P>
   HORMEL (Washington) _ In the wake of the apparent failure of the
Senate to approve gay rights advocate James C. Hormel as ambassador
to Luxembourg, the Clinton administration is considering whether to
resubmit the nomination next year. By JUDY HOLLAND. (Will update)
</P>
