<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-16 16:28 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1501 &Cx1f; taf-z
s l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-ROLEX-ENVY-$ADV18-NYT     10-16 1116
