<P>
   JARDINES _ In hot business news, salsa manufacturerJardine's
Texas Foods has lassoed competitor Best of the West for an
undisclosed price. Bartlesville, Okla.-based Best of the West,
manufacturer of the Buckaroo brand, will bring its 27 salsas,
sauces, jellies and soups to fast-growing Jardine's. They will join
the 20 products sold by 19-year-old Jardine's _ products
likeJailhouse Caviar and Hotter 'N Hell Habanera. (Breyer, Austin
American-Statesman). 6-8. WITH PHOTO.
</P>
