   MILITIA-FORT-HOOD-PLOT _ We focus on Bradley Playford Glover and
Michael Leonard Dorsett, the two men who were arrested last year on
their way to attack Fort Hood and who pleaded guilty in September.
This was one of dozens of domestic terrorist plots thwarted by
police since the Oklahoma City bombing. (Tanamachi, Austin
American-Statesman)
</P>
<P>
   GANG-CIRCLE _ The Travis County DA's office has suggested using
a type of mediation based on Native American peace circles to work
out its controversial gang injunction. Last week, Ronnie Earle's
office called lawyers for the five defendants and told them if they
participate in a circle with community members _ in which each
person stands up and says whatever is on their mind and the
community can ask the defendants to do things to make amends _
prosecutors will drop the injunction. (Harmon, Austin
American-Statesman)
</P>
