<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-16 18:09 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1842 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-MICROSOFT-JUDGE-1STLE     10-16 0763
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MICROSOFT-JUDGE-1STLEDE-$ADV19 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    MICROSOFT JUDGE REGARDED AS TOUGH BUT FAIR
 &HT;    Eds: corrects ``worst lawyers'' to ``worst judges'' in 4th graf
from end.
 &HT;    With MICROSOFT-BIOBOX. Moving in (w) Washington and (f)
financial categories for release Monday, Oct. 19.
 &HT;    A black and white file photo of Judge Thomas Penfield Jackson
photo is available in the National folder on the Cox server.
 &HT;    By MARY BETH REGAN
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
