   DIGITAL-THEATER (Los Angeles) _The just-begun, $385 million
Hollywood &AMP; Highland project wrapping around Mann's Chinese Theatre
promises to be a showcase that will restore some of Hollywood
Boulevard's tarnished glitz, but tucked within the project's
fabulous design is some interesting technology whose effects should
delight movie buffs all over the world. By David Bloom. (Will move
